title: Woodcutting/Level up table
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Woodcutting/Level up table
LevelNew abilities
Each level
  • Each level in Woodcutting slightly increases a player's chance of successfully chopping trees
  • Increases the chance of getting the Beaver pet drop; increases at 200 million experience
  • Gives better logs when chopping Ents
  • Using the special attack on a/an 3rd age axe/dragon axe/infernal axe/crystal axe will boost your Woodcutting level by 3
